description: The fund's objective is to provide investors with a total return, taking into account both capital and income returns, which reflects, before fees and expenses, the returnofthe Fidelity US Quality Income Index. For currency hedged share classes, the return will be hedged to the base currency of the relevant share class. For full details of the objectives please refer to the Key Information Document (KID)and the Prospectus.
name: Fidelity US Quality Income UCITS ETF ACC-GBP (hedged)
